♪ <i> People say...</i> ♪

20:25.491 --> 20:26.913
Oh, damn it, it's everywhere.

20:26.968 --> 20:28.601
It's fine, just leave it.

20:28.703 --> 20:30.217
No, I can't do it, I'm out.

